2. Install boost

- download boost: boost_1_82_0.tar.gz
https://www.boost.org/users/download/

- install
https://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_69_0/more/getting_started/unix-variants.html#easy-build-and-install

cd boost_1_82_0
sudo ./b2 cxxflags="-std=c++14" install
output:
ls /usr/local/lib/libboost_*
ls /usr/local/include/boost